name beamertheme-csh
category Package
revision 76967
shortdesc A Beamer presentation theme for the Complexity Science Hub Vienna
longdesc This package provides a Beamer theme following the corporate
longdesc design of the Complexity Science Hub (CSH) Vienna. It includes
longdesc a title page, automatic section slides, source citation
longdesc commands, and a closing slide with QR code. The theme uses TeX
longdesc Gyre Heros as the default font.
